    .container
      section.about
        p We aim to make advanced AI art generation accessible to everyone. Powered by the cutting-edge Stable Diffusion model, our platform allows users to turn text-based prompts into stunning visuals. Whether you're an artist, designer, or someone who loves to explore creativity, our tool is built for you.
        
      section.features
        h2 Why Stable Diffusion?
        p Stable Diffusion is an advanced AI model specifically designed to generate high-quality images from text inputs. It uses deep learning techniques to understand and generate complex artistic styles, from photorealism to abstract art.

      section.learn-more
        h2 Learn More
        p Explore our GitHub repository for code, updates, and future developments. Collaborate with our community to push the boundaries of AI-generated art.
        p Join us on 
          a(href="https://github.com/Hrushikesh-Reddy/team") GitHub

